**Aëla Labbé** is a photographer who oozes confidence for someone her age.

Her work consists of delicately constructed scenes, filled with poignancy and devotion, while being thoroughly manacling throughout. Her latest set of photo’s rather dramatically deal with the relationship between humanity and nature. check them out above and check out more of her photos on her [Flickr.](http://www.flickr.com/photos/aela/)
